SUMMARY:Competitive Ride (A+) - LM Bossler Blast (38R)
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nAnticipated average pace:
  **20+ mph**\n\nCue and GPX link: [https://ridewithgps.com/routes/30103567
 ](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/30103567)\n\n**This ride is intended for 
 the experienced group rider in good physical condition and capable of main
 taining a steady pace. Few stops if any. Riders unable to maintain the pac
 e may be dropped. If unsure if this ride is for you\, it is recommended yo
 u try the "A" ride option first.**\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. P
 lease bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/
 CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we 
 require an LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n\
 nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https://
 www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYour
  RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://l
 ancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_
 id=323984)\,\n\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/c
 ontent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3140253
 02/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260329T230801Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260329T230801Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
