  do his/her best to keep the group together with regroupings and a sweeper
  may also be appointed at the start. **Please do not join this ride if you
  are not willing to stick with the group.** If maintaining an 18-20mph ave
 rage is beyond your current ability level\, please consider joining an "Ad
 vanced" ride first.\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No earbuds. Please bring wat
 er and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator).\
 n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\, we require an LBC 
