 e/bv-brownstown-akron-farmersville-long-24f/)\n\nThis is an Intermediate C
  Class ride. The ride leader will ride at the advertised average speed. Th
 is is intended to be a group ride with a no-drop rule as the main goal. Th
 e ride leader will do his/her best to keep the group together with occasio
 nal regroupings and/or splitting into multiple groups to align to pace cap
