  agreement to abide by the club's Code of Conduct: [Code of Conduct](https
 ://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module
 _id=323984)\n\nGuidance if an incident occurs: [Incident Actions](https://
 lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=326
 137)
